    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">12</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Application</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Applying Understanding: Texican Identity Today</h2><ul><li>Consider how historical terms influence modern Texas identity</li><li>Recognize ongoing cultural legacies of Texicans</li><li>Reflect on the importance of historical terminology in contemporary discussions</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Understanding 'Texican' helps appreciate the cultural heritage and identity debates in modern Texas communities. <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s7\">[7]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s6\">[6]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Modern descendants of Texicans may identify with this heritage distinct from broader Texan identity.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Reflect on how historical identities shape present-day cultural and political discussions in Texas.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Assuming historical terms have no relevance to contemporary identity.</p></div></div>",
