    "num": "36",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">36</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Transfer</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Connecting Texican Political History to Modern Identity</h2><ul><li>Texican political struggles influenced Texas statehood</li><li>Modern Texan identity reflects this complex heritage</li><li>Understanding history informs contemporary cultural discussions</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">The political conflicts involving Texicans laid foundations for Texas independence and statehood, shaping modern Texan identity and cultural narratives (s2, s7). <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s2\">[2]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s7\">[7]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Modern debates about Texan identity often reference historical Texican experiences.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Reflect on how Texican political history influences current Texas cultural identity.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Separating historical Texican identity from modern Texan culture.</p></div></div>",
